Trade/Device Name(s): Clever Chek TD-4226 Blood Glucose Monitoring System
Specimen Type(s): Fresh capillary whole blood (finger, palm, forearm, upper-arm, calf, thigh)
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Achtung and Clever Chek blood glucose monitoring systems for quantitative measurement of glucose in capillary whole blood.
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for quantitative measurement of glucose in fresh capillary whole blood from finger and alternative sites, for use by healthcare professionals and people with diabetes at home to aid monitoring of diabetes control; not for diagnosis or screening of diabetes, or for neonates.
